( .forthrc )
( FORTH initialisation file, read at start-up [at end of COLD] )

CASE-INSENSITIVE ( make Dictionary lookup be case-insensitive )

( Load Utility words )
?LOAD" utils.fth"
[IF] ." Loaded utils.fth" CR [THEN]

( Load Random Number words )
?LOAD" random.fth"
[IF] ." Loaded random.fth" CR [THEN]

( Load Play words )
?LOAD" play.fth"
[IF] ." Loaded play.fth" CR [THEN]
